column2: an A.M. Eatery////Food: COME HUNGRY. I ordered the Benny Duo (Ham Benedict III
column4: hash browns). This can easily be shared with 2 people...but I'm selfish and have a bottomless pit. Probably enough calories for the week
column5: but super delicious overall. They have this green hot sauce from Austin I love
